In a medium saucepan combine coffee, 2 inches stick cinnamon, allspice, and orange peel. Bring to boiling; reduce heat. Cover and simmer for 5 minutes. Remove solids from coffee with a slotted spoon. Pour coffee into coffee cups. If desired, garnish with cinnamon sticks. Iced Spicy Coffee: Prepare Spicy Coffee as above, except thoroughly chill coffee after simmering. To serve, pour coffee over ice in tall glasses.